{"tid":2490621,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"【畢業即失業】兒子高級文憑畢業呻難搵工無業1年　港媽心酸：成個人冇晒自信心","createTime":"2021-04-15T17:40:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-15T20:10:15.000Z","uid":112551,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ee4f8cb04d7e56cfb4d488b4c17faf8401b0c15f","tid":2490621,"uid":112551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T17:40:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2930000/2930500/son_thumb_20210413_J_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2930000%2F2930500%2Fson_thumb_20210413_J_1024.jpg&h=fce94a0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.baby-kingdom.com/forum.php?mod=viewthread&amp;tid=23449173\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.baby-kingdom.com%2Fforum.php%3Fmod%3Dviewthread%26tid%3D23449173&d=Uh5SjXth0XRRLWSKrhPNwJLurRSHZiEGX9rhKonVocs%3D&h=19f49e38\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.baby-kingdom.com/forum.php?mod=viewthread&amp;tid=23449173</a><br />\n<br />\n本港失業率持續高企，政府上月公布去年12月至今年2月的失業率，達到7.2%，為2004年以來高位。一名港媽日前在網上討論區「親子王國」發文，指兒子畢業1年多，卻一直找不到工作，因而失去自信。<br />\n<br />\n該名港媽在文中指出，兒子是位高級文憑畢業生，由上年畢業到現在，都找不到工作，失業1年多。港媽起初以為是兒子要求高，但和他傾談之後發現，現時市道差，難找到工作。眼見兒子因此失去自信，港媽感心酸，<br />\n<br />\n呢年幾佢成日覺得自己好差，冇晒自信心，見佢咁我都好心酸。<br />\n<br />\n網民：做兼職儲經驗<br />\n<br />\n對於港媽兒子的經歷，不少網民表示同情，指現時經濟不好，「好少請無經驗的後生仔」、「唔好唔開心，大環境問題，非純粹個人因素」、「朋友個仔上年科大畢業，都係啱啱返第一份工」。<br />\n<br />\n有網民建議樓主兒子找兼職工作，「都可以學下待人接物，同避免有空窗期」、「咩都做住先，邊做邊搵自己理想嘅工作」；亦有網民建議樓主兒子繼續進修，待經濟環境好一點才找工作。"},{"pid":"23829b3860609baf5f46e558ecaf624b9311dbd6","tid":2490621,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T17:43:50.000Z","msg":"hd=f6 grad"},{"pid":"7180002e45065680573ad0c43c2aa05cdd42655e","tid":2490621,"uid":49085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T17:49:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1d43ff4b4ff938a10c2990fa2d81c799949ee0b","tid":2490621,"uid":54927,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T17:51:30.000Z","msg":"大把倉務請人"},{"pid":"c0804b34d89876934db76ab1c061add0546f0b77","tid":2490621,"uid":184581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T17:52:43.000Z","msg":"我間公司長期請人 冇人見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f576f831180279bc3971085d639cc227fefc392c","tid":2490621,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c0804b34d89876934db76ab1c061add0546f0b77","tid":2490621,"uid":184581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T17:52:43.000Z","msg":"我間公司長期請人 冇人見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T17:54:58.000Z","msg":"邊行？"},{"pid":"eda68ba06151d3c126ac7a55ba6beb0d19f216d4","tid":2490621,"uid":184581,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f576f831180279bc3971085d639cc227fefc392c","tid":2490621,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c0804b34d89876934db76ab1c061add0546f0b77","tid":2490621,"uid":184581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T17:52:43.000Z","msg":"我間公司長期請人 冇人見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T17:54:58.000Z","msg":"邊行？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T17:56:28.000Z","msg":"PCCW"},{"pid":"26309ac514a390d6462b2661fe2c32ee2987e057","tid":2490621,"uid":112551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T20:08:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7f2588e7e9a782dd099f27aea4c3e13e41fe50d","tid":2490621,"uid":336645,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T20:10:15.000Z","msg":"個仔自己廢姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />正常人HD grad都升到UGC"}]}